This paper is about network updates, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the challenges of implementing updates correctly, which is related to computer security (cs.CR) and control systems (cs.SY). The tool presented in the paper uses algorithms to navigate through the space of possible solutions, which is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the tool is implemented in OCaml, which is a programming language (cs.PL).
